data.description: Nestled perfectly between the charming towns of Fredericksburg and Culpeper, this home offers the pinnacle of suburban living. Located in a serene community, this residence boasts an impressive 2700 square feet of living space, providing an abundance of room for comfortable living.  With 3 generously sized bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms on the main level, this home is a haven of spaciousness and convenience. Whether you have a passion for culinary artistry or simply enjoy cooking for loved ones, the recently updated kitchen features new appliances that cater to your every culinary need.  The interior of this home has been thoughtfully designed and meticulously maintained. Freshly painted in a soft, neutral color palette, it exudes a welcoming atmosphere. New flooring and carpeting underfoot ensure both comfort throughout, accessibility and ease of living are prioritized.  The lower level of this home is a versatile space, complete with its own bedroom and full bathroom. This area offers endless possibilities, from a private guest suite to an entertainment hub with a spacious recreational room.  This beautiful residence is not only a testament to comfortable living but also a gateway to community amenities. Situated in close proximity to the community pool and playground, you'll have access to leisure and recreation right at your doorstep.  Practical updates have also been made to enhance your living experience. The heat pump  2020 and HVAC 2020 system have energy efficiency and optimal climate control. Additionally, a new hot water tank 2023 ensures a constant supply of warm water for your daily needs.  In a highly sought-after location, this home is a rare gem that won't be available for long. Come and experience the joys of living in the vibrant community of Locust Grove, where comfort, style, and convenience come together in perfect harmony. Don't miss the opportunity to make this splendid property your own.
